OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGenetic testing: Babies    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwith rare illnesses given  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fhope                       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Dozens of babies with rare illnesses   
OL,6, have been given "new hope" since Wales 
OL,7, became the first part of the UK to     
OL,8, offer genetic testing two years ago.   
OL,10,FChildren who are seriously ill in      
OL,11,Fhospital can be considered for a test  
OL,12,Fthat reads their entire DNA code.      
OL,14,FIt has led to a diagnosis in 40% of    
OL,15,Fcases, experts said, and a "great leap 
OL,16,Fforward" in their treatment.           
OL,18,FIt is now hoped the test can be        
OL,19,Fextended to more children with a       
OL,20,Fsuspected genetic illness.             
